				<section class="has-el-gap el-gap-default elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-00c579c elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="00c579c" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cabb8e2" data-id="cabb8e2" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c83e9aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-appluxe_core_content" data-id="c83e9aa" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="appluxe_core_content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					        <div class="alhp-sec alhp-core" style="--ac:#ff3b3b;">
            <div class="alhp-wrap">
                <div class="alhp-sec-lbl" style="color:#ff3b3b;">Deep Dive</div>
                <div class="alhp-core-grid">
                                        <article class="alhp-core-card">
                        <div class="alhp-core-head">
                            <span class="alhp-core-num" style="color:#ff3b3b;background:#ff3b3b18;">01</span>
                            <span class="alhp-core-icon">🧠</span>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="alhp-core-h2">What Exactly is Agentic AI?</h2>
                        <div class="alhp-core-body"><p>Traditional AI responds to a single prompt and stops. <strong>Agentic AI</strong> goes further — it breaks goals into sub-tasks, plans actions, calls external APIs, monitors results, and iterates until the objective is achieved.</p><ul><li>Operates with persistent memory and long-horizon reasoning</li><li>Autonomously selects tools and APIs to complete tasks</li><li>Self-corrects when results don't match the objective</li></ul></div>
                    </article>
                                        <article class="alhp-core-card">
                        <div class="alhp-core-head">
                            <span class="alhp-core-num" style="color:#ff3b3b;background:#ff3b3b18;">02</span>
                            <span class="alhp-core-icon">📈</span>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="alhp-core-h2">The 2026 Shift: Why Now?</h2>
                        <div class="alhp-core-body"><p>Three inflection points have made Agentic AI practical at scale:</p><ul><li><strong>Large Action Models (LAMs)</strong> — purpose-built for executing multi-step actions, not just text.</li><li><strong>Long-term context memory</strong> — models retain millions of tokens, enabling multi-day tasks.</li><li><strong>Mature API ecosystems</strong> — every SaaS product now exposes APIs for agent consumption.</li></ul></div>
                    </article>
                                        <article class="alhp-core-card">
                        <div class="alhp-core-head">
                            <span class="alhp-core-num" style="color:#ff3b3b;background:#ff3b3b18;">03</span>
                            <span class="alhp-core-icon">⚡</span>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="alhp-core-h2">How Agentic AI Improves Efficiency</h2>
                        <div class="alhp-core-body"><p>Businesses deploying agentic workflows report dramatic reductions in manual overhead:</p><ul><li>Eliminates repetitive, rule-based tasks consuming skilled employee time</li><li>Orchestrates multi-system workflows (CRM → email → Slack → billing) automatically</li><li>Executes tasks 24/7 at machine speed with consistent quality</li></ul></div>
                    </article>
                                        <article class="alhp-core-card">
                        <div class="alhp-core-head">
                            <span class="alhp-core-num" style="color:#ff3b3b;background:#ff3b3b18;">04</span>
                            <span class="alhp-core-icon">🛒</span>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="alhp-core-h2">Impact on the SaaS Landscape</h2>
                        <div class="alhp-core-body"><p>Agentic AI is reshaping how SaaS products are built, sold, and priced:</p><ul><li><strong>API-first architecture</strong> — every feature exposed for agent consumption</li><li><strong>AI-ready platforms</strong> — native hooks for LLM orchestration layers</li><li><strong>Outcome-based pricing</strong> — charging per task completed, not per seat</li></ul></div>
                    </article>
                                    </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        				</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
		</section>
