						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2335a58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-appluxe_trust" data-id="2335a58" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="appluxe_trust.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					        <div class="alhp-sec alhp-trust" style="--ac:#ff3b3b;">
            <div class="alhp-wrap">
                <div class="alhp-trust-in">
                    <div class="alhp-trust-txt">
                        <div class="alhp-sec-lbl" style="color:#ff3b3b;">Safety &amp; Control</div>
                        <h2 class="alhp-trust-h2">Overcoming the Trust Gap: Human-in-the-Loop</h2>
                        <div class="alhp-trust-body"><p>The most powerful Agentic AI deployments don't remove humans — they <strong>position humans as strategic supervisors</strong>. High-stakes decisions trigger approval gates before execution.</p><p>This Human-in-the-Loop (HITL) architecture ensures compliance with regulatory requirements, maintains brand control, and builds the organisational trust needed for AI adoption at scale.</p></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="alhp-pillars">
                                                <div class="alhp-pillar">
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-icon">🛡️</div>
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-info">
                                <strong>Compliance Ready</strong>
                                <span>All AI actions are logged, auditable, and aligned with regulatory frameworks.</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                                <div class="alhp-pillar">
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-icon">👁️</div>
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-info">
                                <strong>Full Transparency</strong>
                                <span>Every agent decision is explainable with a clear, reviewable reasoning trail.</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                                <div class="alhp-pillar">
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-icon">⚡</div>
                            <div class="alhp-pillar-info">
                                <strong>Rapid Override</strong>
                                <span>Humans can pause, modify, or override any agentic workflow in real time.</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                                            </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
